headline: C.H. Robinson Unveils New Generation of Logistics Management Solutions
summary: EDEN PRAIRIE, Minn., November 13, 2024--C.H. Robinson (Nasdaq: CHRW), the global leader in third-party logistics (3PL) and fourth-party logistics (4PL) services, with 35 million shipments and $22 billion in freight managed annually, today announced the launch of C.H. Robinson Managed Solutions™, the next generation of logistics management. This innovation will solve a growing gap in the market for shippers wanting seamless access to cutting-edge TMS technology, 3PL managed transportation and 4PL
